avel-1068x362.jpg 1068w\"></a></p><h3>Availability</h3><p>Alchemy Bicycles are taking pre-orders for the 2021 Arktos now, with bikes available in May 2021. Frames are sold with a lifetime warranty. Get it in Charcoal/Sunburst, Gray/Light Gray or Sand/Burnt Orange colorways. Head to the Alchemy Bicycles website for full details on build specifications.</p><p><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NVx0K2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>AlchemyBicycles.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"2490b2dfd7a2c02de3608610877d29534aef3984cca994487da3db77c28eb2b0","category":"Cycling"}